quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  1,2,sab terhan ki tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar ) hai jo tamam makhloqaat ka perwar-digaar hai
  1,3,bara meharban nihayat reham wala
  1,4,insaaf ke din ka haakim
  1,5,( ae perwar-digaar ) hum teri hi ibadat karte hain aur tujh hi se madad mangte hain
  1,6,hum ko seedhay raste chala
  1,7,un logon ke raste jin par to apna fazlo karam karta raha nah un ke jin par ghusse hota raha aur nah gumrahon ke
